            ]
          },
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Title": "What is Death-Valley Reborn?",
              "Note": "A quick overview for new arrivals.",
              "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Text": "Death-Valley Reborn is a community-driven ARK: Survival Ascended cluster built around cinematic events, long-term dino legacies, collaborative storytelling, and respectful PvP. We encourage shenanigans, but we protect player time and creativity.\n\nUse the tabs above to learn our PvP rules, building etiquette, shiny protocols, and community code before you truly step into the Valley.",
                  "FontSize": 13,
                  "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "PvP Guidelines",
          "Note": "Fight for glory, not for grief.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.2, 0.05, 0.0, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Core PvP Rules",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• PvP is allowed for breeding and dino purposes only.\n• Raids are permitted only if BOTH parties agree.\n• Use the #battle-time-raids Discord channel to schedule day and time.\n• No offline raiding — respect others’ time, effort, and creativity.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.35, 0.12, 0.05, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Raid Conduct",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Raids must be scheduled and agreed upon — no surprise base wipes.\n• Focus on objectives, not total destruction.\n• Give your opponents something to rebuild with.\n• If raid rules are broken repeatedly, admins may intervene with wipes, dino confiscation, or timeouts.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.4, 0.18, 0.08, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Traps, Turrets, and Defenses",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Plant traps and defenses must be set to target wild dinos only under normal conditions.\n• If you are preparing for a raid and need to change settings, you must announce it in server chat so others can steer clear.\n• Do not weaponize PvE areas against unsuspecting players.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Title": "Examples of Acceptable PvP",
                  "Note": "Click to expand for clarity.",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Organized dino breeding fights.\n• Agreed-upon tribe skirmishes.\n• Scheduled raids with clear start/end times.\n\nNot okay:\n• Offline base wiping.\n• Ambushing players who never agreed to PvP.\n• Repeated harassment of the same tribe or player.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "Building Etiquette",
          "Note": "Build like you’re making the map better.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.3, 0.15, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Base & Outpost Limits",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Each tribe may claim ONE main base location per map.\n• Each tribe may also build up to TWO small outposts per map.\n• Outposts must stay compact (2x2 or 4x4 style footprint).\n• Use outposts for utility, travel, or resource touchpoints — not full second bases.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.35, 0.2, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Respecting Space & Sightlines",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Do not build too close to other players’ bases.\n• Give room for expansion and creativity.\n• Don’t box players in or wall off key routes.\n• Think of the map as a shared canvas — your build should enhance it.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.38, 0.22, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Caves, Artifacts, and Resources",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Do not block caves that contain resources or artifacts.\n• Avoid walling off high-value resource spawns.\n• If your build unintentionally blocks access, adjust it when requested.\n• Artifact runs and progression spots must stay accessible to the cluster.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Title": "Spam & Performance",
                  "Note": "What counts as spam?",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• No pillar spam or random foundations stretched across the map.\n• No needless single pillars to “claim” land you’re not using.\n• Avoid excessive decorative spam that tanks FPS or causes stutter.\n\nRule of thumb: if your build noticeably lags the area or exists only to block others, it’s a problem.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "Teleports & Resources",
          "Note": "Shared access keeps the Valley alive.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.3, 0.15, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Public Teleports",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Every tribe must have at least ONE public teleport outside their main base.\n• This helps new and returning players navigate the Valley.\n• Do not hide your only public teleport behind killboxes or killzones.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.35, 0.2, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Cave & Artifact Teleports",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Only ONE teleport is allowed outside each cave or artifact cave entrance.\n• If one already exists, do not place another.\n• All cave teleports must be UNLOCKED and PUBLIC.\n• These are for the whole cluster, not one tribe.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.38, 0.22, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Public Sap Taps",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Every tribe must maintain at least ONE unlocked tree sap tap for public use.\n• Use this to help reduce spam and keep shared resources flowing.\n• If your public tap is destroyed or moved, replace it in a reasonable time.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Title": "Why Shared Access Matters",
                  "Note": "Click for philosophy.",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Death-Valley is built on cooperation layered over competition. Shared teleports and resources keep the world feeling alive, reduce clutter, and help new players actually join the story instead of bouncing off a wall of inconvenience.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "Shiny Dino Protocol",
          "Note": "Rare beasts, clear rules.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.25, 0.08, 0.02, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Claim Limits",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• You may only claim ONE shiny per person at a time.\n• You must wait for that shiny to be tamed or killed before moving to another.\n• Eggs do not need to be claimed, but parents do if you are going to tame or kill them.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.32, 0.1, 0.03, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "How to Claim a Shiny",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• You must physically be at the shiny and see it.\n• Make sure no one else is in the area already working it.\n• Claim it in general chat BEFORE you interact (move, damage, KO).\n• Use: Claim [Name of Shiny] + one clarifying detail.\n  Example: “Claim Taser Rex on SE”\n• Use the in-game name; short forms are okay only if unambiguous.\n  Not okay: names like “Meg” that can mean multiple dinos.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.36, 0.13, 0.04, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "During & After the Claim",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• You must have everything you need on you when you claim.\n• If you die, run out of mats, or leave render, you lose the claim and must unclaim in chat.\n• You can reclaim by starting over and following all rules again.\n• If you knock out or claim a KO’d shiny, you must stay with it until it tames, wakes, or dies.\n• If you find an abandoned KO shiny, contact an admin before killing.\n• If the original player doesn’t return within ~10 minutes, another player may claim it.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0.4, 0.16, 0.05, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Transfers, Mistakes, and Enforcement",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• You may give your claim to another player, but you must unclaim and they must claim in chat BEFORE they tame/kill.\n• If you accidentally kill a shiny, say so in chat and explain.\n• If you tame without claiming, an admin may confiscate or kill the dino.\n• Calling out a shiny without being at its coords is against the rules.\n\nBreaking these shiny rules more than 3 times can result in a 24-hour ban.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "Community Code",
          "Note": "The Valley is shared. Act like it.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.3, 0.15, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Respect the Realm",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Respect all players — this is a shared realm.\n• No harassment, hate speech, or targeted toxicity.\n• Disagreements happen; harassment doesn’t have to.\n• If you’re frustrated, step away or ask an admin to help mediate.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.35, 0.2, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Performance & Lag",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Help keep lag down and gameplay smooth.\n• Be mindful of dino counts, spam, and constantly running machines.\n• If an admin asks you to adjust something for performance, work with them.\n• A smoother Valley is better for everyone’s stories.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.38, 0.22, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "Shenanigans Welcome",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Shenanigans are welcome — we’re here to have fun.\n• Keep it fair, mythic, and tribe-worthy.\n• Don’t cross the line into griefing or targeted bullying.\n• If your fun ruins someone else’s night, it’s not the right kind of fun.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "Admin Contact",
          "Note": "We’re here to help, not to DM camp.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.3, 0.15, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "How to Reach Admins",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Do NOT DM admins directly for server issues.\n• Use #bobs-with-probs in Discord or in-game server chat to tag admins.\n• This keeps support organized and visible to the whole team.\n• You’ll usually get faster help when it’s all in one place.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.35, 0.2, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "What to Include in a Report",
                      "FontSize": 18,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 5]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "• Who is involved (player/tribe names).\n• What happened, and where (map + coords if possible).\n• When it happened.\n• Screenshots or clips if you have them.\n\nClear info = faster, fairer help.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Title": "Why We Avoid DMs",
                  "Note": "Click to expand.",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "DMs are easy to lose, hard to track, and put pressure on individual admins instead of the team.\nBy keeping all support in shared channels, we protect you, we protect the admins, and we keep a clear record if we ever need to revisit an incident.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Category_v1.DU_Panel_Category_v1_C",
        "Props": {
          "Title": "Lore & Mythos",
          "Note": "For those who listen to the Valley.",
          "Fill": 1
        },
        "UIItems": [
          {
            "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1.DU_Panel_VerticalScrollBox_v1_C",
            "Props": {
              "Fill": 1
            },
            "UIItems": [
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Text": "The Rebirth of the Valley",
                  "FontSize": 22,
                  "Justification": "Center",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
                }
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Border_v1.DU_Panel_Border_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Color": [0, 0.3, 0.15, 1],
                  "Padding": [10, 10, 10, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "In the ashes of the old world, a Valley was reborn.\n\nWhat came before was not forgotten — it was reforged. From old save files, broken bases, and memories of cities that once lit the night, Death-Valley rose again as a place where legacy matters.\n\nThis cluster is more than maps and dinos; it’s a living story carried forward by every Survivor who chooses to stay.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [0, 0, 0, 0]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Title": "The Beating Heart",
                  "Note": "A legacy remembered.",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 10]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "This server lives on in loving memory of Grunt — a raiding master and builder of fortresses even when life tried to stop him.\n\nHis spirit sits in the ice walls, the ramparts, the stubbornness to keep pushing when the odds are bad. When you build something beautiful here, when you refuse to give up on a tame or a tribe, you’re keeping that heartbeat going.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Panels/DU_Panel_Group_v1.DU_Panel_Group_v1_C",
                "Props": {
                  "Title": "Your Place in the Story",
                  "Note": "Every tribe carves a chapter.",
                  "Padding": [5, 10, 5, 20]
                },
                "UIItems": [
                  {
                    "Widget": "/Ark-Nucleus/SharedContent/Widgets/Views/DU_View_SimpleText_v1.DU_View_SimpleText_v1_C",
                    "Props": {
                      "Text": "You are not just passing through this Valley.\n\nEvery base, every raid, every alliance and betrayal becomes part of the cluster’s mythos. Build with intention. Fight with style. Leave behind ruins and monuments that make future Survivors wonder who you were.\n\nWelcome to Death-Valley Reborn. Write something worth remembering.",
                      "FontSize": 13,
                      "Padding": [5, 5, 5, 5]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
